  <brief_title>The Efficacy of Topical Minocycline in Managing Symptomatic Oral Lichen Planus</brief_title>
  <official_title>The Efficacy of Topical Minocycline in Managing Symptomatic Oral Lichen Planus. A Randomized Controlled Trial</official_title>
  <sponsors>
